-KzhgrdGrqPZu7OUKowQ.author: Leo N Tolstoy
-KzhgrdGrqPZu7OUKowQ.description: Food fads are grabbing everyone's attention, thanks to the internet fueling us with unlimited information from all around. One of the most interesting food fads we came across was the concept of 'negative calorie' foods. This theory of negative calorie foods suggests that you can have these foods in as much quantity as you want without any weight gain, because digesting these foods may take up more calories than what they actually contain, thereby, nullifying the addition of calories. Basically, the net gain of calories is in negative, hence the name.
-KzhgrdGrqPZu7OUKowQ.shortDescription: The Brew and Barbeque invests Rs 6 crore to unveil outlet in Bengaluru.
-KzhgrdGrqPZu7OUKowQ.title: Can Eating Negative Calorie Foods Help You Lose Weight?

-Kzhh1b7L7HAtv6IxsIw.author: Mark Henry
-Kzhh1b7L7HAtv6IxsIw.description: Avoid eating excess of these foods; instead plan 4-5 small meals that also have these foods included in say, one or two meals through the day. Everything in moderation is beneficial for your health and proper functioning of your body.
-Kzhh1b7L7HAtv6IxsIw.shortDescription: The Brew and Barbeque invests Rs 6 crore to unveil outlet in Bengaluru.
-Kzhh1b7L7HAtv6IxsIw.title: What's the best way to take advantage of negative calorie foods?

-KzhhCgbSykJOas78gxE.author: Mark Henry
-KzhhCgbSykJOas78gxE.description: The theory is that you can eat lots of negative calorie foods in order to lose weight. Some of the examples of negative calorie foods are non-starchy vegetables, high fiber foods, water fruits and vegetables like water-melon and celery among others. So these foods have fewer amounts of calories but require body's energy to support the digestive process, helping you lose weight at the same time.
-KzhhCgbSykJOas78gxE.shortDescription: The Brew and Barbeque invests Rs 6 crore to unveil outlet in Bengaluru.
-KzhhCgbSykJOas78gxE.title: What's the theory behind Negative Calorie Foods?
